    "is_free": false,
    "description": "欢迎游玩这个步步新奇的东方大陆。在这里玩家将扮演一名刀笔吏——萧辰，在天下倾颓、诸侯割据的时代，萧辰背上行囊，游历东南西北，探索山海秘境、见识无数宝物，结识众多神奇有趣的伙伴，当然，也会遭遇强大的敌人……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>【不一样的东方大世界】</li></ul>狐国、密库、衣锦城、驼母宫、博望馆、龙府、人鱼岛、冰夷渡、古战场、高耳山、北境村庄等等，游历不一样的山川河流、秘境洞窟带来的别样氛围。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/ed387031950697c043adfb223da81578.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/97ccbe51c72b9d37732ff85548a4a5ae.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/4c877ffd1102aa013f21008f8c70d967.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/361a60c61756ce2d5cd632ef2954d01a.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/80cc7af3ea9cfdf97bd3736a48197751.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>【沉浸式体验海量剧情】</li></ul>丰富世界观和故事细节，希望能有大量支线填充。领略当地的风土人情，并且完成他们的委托来增加代入感，以及世界观的可信度。同时，游戏文案的整体风格会朝部分写实的方向靠拢，给玩家带真实的体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/13e09997277b7a1dffe67d3fe9b669d8.poster.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/13e09997277b7a1dffe67d3fe9b669d8.webm?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/13e09997277b7a1dffe67d3fe9b669d8.mp4?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/bc92cd1d4fa11e09fcd3c45b7679ffbf.poster.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/bc92cd1d4fa11e09fcd3c45b7679ffbf.webm?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/bc92cd1d4fa11e09fcd3c45b7679ffbf.mp4?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>【史官视角下的别样玩法】</li></ul>”史官”作为一个罕见的角色定位，我们将围绕他做出一系列的系统包装，给予玩家新颖的体验。在每章节的最后，当玩家探访完该区域的主线内容，将出现【记述】功能，玩家可以对该国作出客观或不客观的评价。<br>当玩家结束游戏全流程，将获得一本只属于自己的【史书草稿】，不同的评价将直接影响结局。<br>-总是能给出客观理智的中立评价——“史官结局”<br>-受感情影响，无法直书亲近之人所作之恶——“归隐结局”<br>-无法纵容恶行，弃笔从戎——“游侠结局” 等<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/8987a54da297bc1f929b42acf4fc3ece.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/4bafa1b0ffe5cc3d2fc2c55a85eb4015.poster.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/4bafa1b0ffe5cc3d2fc2c55a85eb4015.webm?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/4bafa1b0ffe5cc3d2fc2c55a85eb4015.mp4?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>【动作战棋视觉盛宴】</li></ul>易上手的拼图操作——战斗中合并移动和释放技能的操作，降低操作门槛。简单化思考逻辑，将更多注意力放在伤害最大化上以及战斗核心上。<br>割草般爽快战斗——技能效果强力，敌人配置多样，角色配合多，机制协调策略丰富<br>及时的正反馈和压力释放——攒能量释放大招清屏战场内的敌人，精英敌人的预告和打断机制丰富策略玩法和取舍判断。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/ab39003a52b9de941954117228e32c81.poster.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/ab39003a52b9de941954117228e32c81.webm?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/ab39003a52b9de941954117228e32c81.mp4?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/60eef199e55cdcc35c8659df43fafc18.poster.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/60eef199e55cdcc35c8659df43fafc18.webm?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/60eef199e55cdcc35c8659df43fafc18.mp4?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/f06f2f9f714ee7d92336b518731d8895.poster.avif?t=1701306834\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/f06f2f9f714ee7d92336b518731d8895.webm?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363230/extras/f06f2f9f714ee7d92336b518731d8895.mp4?t=1701306834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
